      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "* Wiꞥſch irr jawu * ſtaiſtu Glihtumu jauki iſgresnojs/ bet tee irr jawu Negantibu Bil-des un Apgahnſchanaſ tur ee-zehluſchi. Tapehz darrischu eſ wiꞥſchem to par Netchkihſtibu."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es nodohſchu to Sweſcheem Rohkâ par Laupijumu/ un teem Besdeewigeem wirs Semmes/ ka tee to aplaupa/ un ka tee to tagahna."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir mannu Waigu grib-bu es no teem atgreest/ ka tee mannu apſlehptu Weetu ſagah-na/ un Pohſtitaji nahks pahr to/ un ſagahnihs to."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Darri weenu Schkehdi/ jo ta Semme trr pilla ar Afins-Wainahm/ un tas Pilſtahts pils ar Warras-Darba."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz atweddiſchu es tohs niknakus no teem Paga-neem/ kas winzu Nammus ce-utantohs/ un liſchu to Lepnibu to Warreno mittetees/ un ſa-gahniſchu winnu twehtas Wee-tas."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Iſdeldeſchana nahk/ un tee meklehs Meeru/ bet ne-waid."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Behdas pahr Behdahm ka weenu Rohku/ un ſagrahbe"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehniſch behdafees/ un tee Leel-Kungi buhs ar Iſ-truhzinaschann apgehrbti/ un tahs Rohkas to Lauschu tahs Semmes nogurs. Es darrischu teem pehz winnu Zelfkeim/ un pehz winno Nopelnu gribbu es tohs tohdiht/ un tee fajuttihſ/ ka es efimu tas KUNGGA."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas notike feſta Gaddâ/ feſta Mehneſi/ prektâ Deenâ tas Meh-nes/ kad es jawâ Nammuâ jehe-deju/ un tee Wezzajee no Ju-h-da manna Preektchâ fehdeja/ tad kritte tur ta Kllnga KUNG-GA Rohka pahr manni."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es redſeju/ un rangi/ tur bija weens/ ka Gihmts ta patt ka Ugguns bija/ no winna Gurneemſeinjup bija tas ta patt ka Ugguns/ un no winna Gur-neem augſchup bija tas/ ka Skaidruins un deggohts Spoh-schums."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch iſſteepe ta patt"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
